ff the tanks then medd and heal when I started my cleric I couldnt beleive some of the spells they got wtf no cleric I ever grouped with told me about these who do you think is gonna know more about your abilities you or someone else no druid to harmony pull? it up to you to offer to soothe and explain how it works explain to them that stun can acctually be more mana efficent than heal there is no reason you cant get involved in the action but your gonna havta speak up if you join a grp and just sit down and med and heal without ever saying youd like to play a different role whoes fault is it? last clerics cant solo? OMG what is wrong sure ya cant go out and square of toe to toe with a mob like a warrior but guess what if ya want to do that make a warrior clerics have more solo techniques available to them than any other class Ive played self buff then remem your spells clerics can reverse kite (probably the best solo technique in the game) they can root and nuke and while we arnt a tank compared to a wizzard we have unbeleivable ac,hp,and mellee skill so why are clerics saying they cant solo? quit being so lazy and play the game use your imagination and above all you dont like the role clerics seam to be stuck in then dont go along with it show them your skills remember if ya aint smiling :) why are ya playing <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;                                                                         Carb the drunken dwarven cleric of torv<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
